502031.desc: Compared to pork buns, shaved ice is tastier. Compared to shaved ice, fireworks are prettier. Compared to fireworks, what I care for the most is...
502031.name: Summer Vacation

401232.desc: Haiyaaah! It's up to you, Ayanami! Oh, Commander! Are you actually keeping score? We might not be having a serious match, but that's no excuse for you to stand around and do nothing.
401232.name: Breezy Doubles

213010.desc: Erebus-class monitor – Erebus, Hull Number I02!
213010.name: Erebus

302110.desc: Mogami-class heavy cruiser number two – Mikuma.
302110.name: Mikuma

201221.desc: I love the bustle of a Sakura festival! Commander, care to try some of Akashi's takoyaki? I've heard their taste is out of this world!
201221.name: Fairly Flavourful Festival

502030.desc: Ning Hai-class Light Cruser, Ping Hai
502030.name: Ping Hai

902012.desc: Happy New Year, again! So, you wanna try sharing this "cross-cupped wine?" What, it's not a drinking game? Welp, I guess I've still got a whole ton to learn about the Dragon Empery's customs~
902012.name: Lush Spring Dreams

401233.desc: Welcome! A table for one today? Um... Commander, my smile doesn’t look stiff... right?
401233.name: Perfect Smile?

102270.desc: Omaha-class light cruiser – Marblehead, Hull Number CL-12.
102270.name: Marblehead

103061.desc: Commander, look, look! This is my handmade Indy plushie! Isn't it utterly adorable?! It's the magnum opus of my work in the Arts & Crafts Club!
103061.name: At School With Indy!

502033.desc: Big sister says that even though we have some money now, we still have to save as much as we can. Um... Anyway, I'm the younger "Dragon Sister," Ping Hai. Erm... I'm kind of hungry. Do you maybe have something to eat?
502033.name: Dragon Sisters! -P

103131.desc: Textbooks, pencils and erasers... hey, must students always pay attention in class... Commander? Can you arrange for us to get more extracurricular activities?
103131.name: Wild Huntress Schoolgirl

902011.desc: Summertime means pool time! Oh, hey, Commander. What are you waiting for? Come over and let's have fun!
902011.name: Pristine Piscene

107221.desc: So this is my new school, huh? Hmm... gotta put my stuff down first before checking in with the teacher.
107221.name: Transfer Student From Afar

107291.desc: Yaaaaawn... Huh!? Commander!? You scared me... I was just going to lie down and... Um, yes, with little Hellcat here... Goodnight...
107291.name: Comfy Cotton Jammies

905012.desc: You damn scalawag... You don't just sneak into someone's hideaway without consequences, ya know. Though, I found this place by pure chance too. Don't go tellin' anyone else about it!
905012.name: Private Après Midi

905013.desc: Bonne année... Or rather, I should say "Happy New Year" here, yes? A year of peace and prosperity passes, and we are here to welcome another... and I must thank you for making that possible.
905013.name: First Snow Upon the Cutlass's Edge

502026.desc: Good boy. Chew thoroughly before you swallow. I never thought I'd help with a charity event for nature, but Da Bao's made a lot of new friends because of it. Keep up the good work, Commander and Ping!
502026.name: Da Bao's Friend!

905011.desc: The guest of honor shouldn't be wandering around looking for girls drinking alone... Hmph, might as well have a drink while you're here anyway.
905011.name: Uninhibited Bloodstone

102271.desc: After trying out a whole bunch of activities, I settled on joinin' the boxing club in the end. Everyone wants to exercise now and then, right? Come along, Commander, and we'll have a fun workout together~
102271.name: Boxing Girl!

101340.desc: Fletcher-class destroyer – Hazelwood, Hull Number DD-531.
101340.name: Hazelwood

502029.desc: Yes! … this feels good. Thank you, Commander. In order to live up to your expectations, from now on, I will be more serious around you, Commander. Hey, don't run!
502029.name: Ning Hai (Retrofit)

105040.desc: Pennsylvania-class Battleship – Arizona, Hull Number BB-39!
105040.name: Arizona

202201.desc: My dear, I changed into the new outfit as per your request. I would be most grateful were you to offer me words of praise, Master.
202201.name: White Rose

105110.desc: Colorado class battleship— West Virginia, hull number BB-48.
105110.name: West Virginia

107220.desc: Independence-class light aircraft carrier – Independence, Hull Number CVL-22.
107220.name: Independence

302109.desc: Are you sure this is a retrofit and not some weird hazing ritual? I look... Well, I suppose I do feel stronger. Guess I'll try to work a bit harder. Wouldn't hurt for you to look forward to it a little.
302109.name: Mogami (Retrofit)

107290.desc: Independence-class light aircraft carrier – Bataan, Hull Number CVL-29.
107290.name: Bataan

900279.desc: 突击者级航空母舰—突击者，舷号CV-4
900279.name: 突击者

203071.desc: The school has recently been consumed by a series of Mysteries... there must be some Mastermind lurking behind the scenes. Yes, another Tribulation awaits me! I shall part the veil and reveal all Truths!
203071.name: Truth Seeker

102132.desc: The Sakura Empire's clothes are just so refined. Ahaha... Aren't you cold standing out there, Commander? Sit down with me and have a drink.
102132.name: Spirits in the Snow

202202.desc: I've received ample advice from my colleagues in the Maid Team regarding swimwear etiquette. My honourable Master, are you pleased with my appearance?
202202.name: Scorching-Hot Seirios

102070.desc: Atlanta-class light cruiser – Juneau, Hull Number CL-52!
102070.name: Juneau

301179.desc: The newly-retrofitted Kagerou has arrived~ I won't let that sister of mine pass me up anymore! Commander, lead us forward towards distant shores!
301179.name: Kagerou (Retrofit)

502022.desc: Happy Mid-Autumn Festival! I heard that if you pray to the moon today, you’ll become as pretty as the Goddess of the Moon! ...Eh? You’re gonna pray too?
502022.name: Moon Palace Rabbit

903021.desc: Oh my, hehe... Are you enjoying the warmth of the sunlight here? I'm glad that you're finding some time to relax here, but wouldn't you rather come play with everyone else?
903021.name: White Sand Paradise

203072.desc: O Unfathomable King of the slumbering depths, hear the call of my Force and step into this world through the Azur Gate! ...Huh, Commander? Why did you show up?
203072.name: Summoner from the Azure Depths

201210.desc: J-class destroyer ー Javelin, Hull Number F61!
201210.name: Javelin

101279.desc: The day has finally arrived~! Bunnies, are you ready? Bailey's debut show is about to begin! Commander, sisters, come and see my bunny magic!
101279.name: Bailey (Retrofit)

202203.desc: I have heard it is part of a maid's duties to dress to her honourable Master's liking over the holidays. Would this outfit happen to... satisfy the honourable Master's wishes?
202203.name: Azure Horizons

301181.desc: I see a chance... to capitalize on the Dragon Empery's famous mooncakes... Commander, would you like to have a taste of the Moon Palace's delicacies? If you buy them in bulk, I'll give you a special discount.
301181.name: Mooncake Merchant

107091.desc: I'm not trying to go anywhere in particular; I just want to enjoy the scenery along the way. Commander, let's go experience the thrills of the road together.
107091.name: A Trip Down Route 66

107223.desc: Whew... A bit of stretching helps keep the body flexible. Hm? I'm in loungewear, what about it? I'd appreciate it if you wouldn't stare too much, though...
107223.name: Liberty and Leisure

401461.desc: The bustling beach, clamoring with waves of joyfulness... experiencing this kind of summer is a first for me, but I don't dislike it...
401461.name: Her First Summer

102133.desc: Oh my, what a good little commander you've been, waiting here all this time for me. Hop in~ Did you think you would be driving? Hehe, you shouldn't underestimate me~
102133.name: Luxurious Wheels

205073.desc: My beautiful Adonis, why dost thou refuseth to take refuge in the trove of everlasting love... Perhaps my outfit can finally pierce thy heart? Hehe~
205073.name: Prestige of the Glorious Formula

502018.desc: Commander, thank you for waiting for me. Though I am unworthy of this honor, thank you so much...
502018.name: Coronal Afterglow

101140.desc: Fletcher-class destroyer - Foote, Hull Number DD-511!
101140.name: Foote

203089.desc: Commander, what do you think? I look more mature than I did before... right?
203089.name: Exeter (Retrofit)

401463.desc: Dancing beams of light, shimmering on-stage; uplifted voices, joined as one by song... Upon this unknown stage, my heart doth flutter... Yet this sensation, is quite refreshing.
401463.name: Star-Lit★Chocolate

502021.desc: Summer’s all about the beach! And the beach is all about good food! Commander, let’s find something delicious to eat!
502021.name: Summer Hunger

107020.desc: Lexington-class aircraft carrier ー Lexington, Hull Number CV-2!
107020.name: Lexington

201212.desc: Everyone, hurry up! We rarely get to go out to play, so let's make every minute count! Javelin packed plenty of lunches, so let's have a picnic by the beach!
201212.name: Beach Picnic!

207062.desc: I heard that the Sakura Empire's traditional attire was really hard to put on... but the Dragon's Empery's outfits are even more... Huh?! Commander, p-please look away!
207062.name: Pungent Plum

10100061.desc: It's good to take it easy and celebrate once in a while, but especially in moments like these, you can't afford to let your guard down. Commander, why don't we spar for a bit? Don't even think about holding back - come at me!
10100061.name: Goddesses' Smile

401462.desc: Through the sweat and tears, striving for your goals. Rejoice in victory, sink within defeat... How fascinating, this "sports meet" may be.
401462.name: Girls' Relay

502020.desc: Ning Hai-class Light Cruiser, Ning Hai
502020.name: Ning Hai

203090.desc: London-class heavy cruiser, Sussex. Hull Number 96.
203090.name: Sussex

107222.desc: Hmm... Isn't this one a bit too garish? Mm... What if we pair it with a necklace or some sort of purse? ...Commander, your thoughts? C'mon, don't just stare at me, give me something to work with here...
107222.name: The Independent Line

303170.desc: Mogami-class heavy cruiser number three – Suzuya.
303170.name: Suzuya

207061.desc: Being able to occasionally have a peaceful school life... is something I could get used to. Commander, look at the markings on this butterfly - aren't they lovely?
207061.name: Glorious School Life

317010.desc: Type A Mod. 2 cruiser submarine – I-13.
317010.name: I-13

401464.desc: "Jianzhi," the art of breathing life into works of cut paper... is a world beyond my imagination. If these decorations are said to usher in blessings... are they akin to a coat-of-arms or a holy seal?
401464.name: Jianzhi Fantasia

203091.desc: What are you spacing out for? Have you not gotten tired of staring at all the swimsuits yet? Good grief... Are you able to help set up the parasol or the beach chairs at least?
203091.name: Sunlit Tulips

306091.desc: Hehe~ If you don't have any other plans, then your only task... is to enjoy a holiday by the sea! Commander, have you switched into vacation mode yet?
306091.name: Shimmering Surf

301189.desc: If you have this much money remaining... then you may visit me and spend it with confidence... A discount, you say...? Of course... Someday, I shall give you one...
301189.name: Shiranui (Retrofit)

203092.desc: What are you staring at me for? I'm just the same as any of the others... Y-you have a few more hands to shake? Of course...
203092.name: Wine and Red Roses

302129.desc: Hmh. Guess I won't be needin' these bandages anymore. Commander, how about we find out how strong I've gotten... by having you take one of my punches?
302129.name: Sendai (Retrofit)

106029.desc: Commander, there's no need to be so afraid. There are only two things my balls hit-- Enemies, and victory! Ah, sometimes they do hit the windows too, ahaha...
106029.name: Bogue (Retrofit)

201216.desc: "Hello, everyone~! I'm Javelin, the new idol who arrived from the Royal Navy! I hope that my songs will be able to bring a smile to everyone's faces, so please take good care of me!" Hehe, how was that for an introduction, Commander?
201216.name: Energetic Idol @120% Motivation!

701021.desc: Comrade Commander, are you here to see my room? Hm? That Шутки isn't funny? Then how about... did my room come to see you, comrade Commander?
701021.name: Bad Bunny Behind Bars

305111.desc: I found quite the nostalgic outfit when I was cleaning my wardrobe. Let's see... "Prepare to come with me on a new journey!" How do I look, Commander?
305111.name: Style of the Sakura Capital

801022.desc: Even though I'm an Iris Libre squire, I'm currently working hard to have a rich student life. Um... maybe this is a bit too laid back?
801022.name: École de Chevalier

801021.desc: It's good to be able to stop and smell the roses every now and then. Um, Commander, would you be able to accompany me a bit longer?
801021.name: Fleur Blanche

202101.desc: Gloucester, light cruiser of the Royal Maids, at your service for the Spring Festival... You say I look displeased? I beg your pardon, it's just... Such holidays are in fact quite busy for the Maids. We have much on our minds. It is none of your concern.
202101.name: Brilliance in Purple

102260.desc: Atlanta-class light cruiser – Reno, Hull Number CL-96.
102260.name: Reno

801023.desc: Good evening, Commander. I am currently enjoying the party in the company of my friends, as my duties as a squire entail. Um... I've had a bit too much to drink? R-really...?
801023.name: Feast of Champagne

303181.desc: It's time for Kumano's sexy swimsuit debut~! Just kidding~☆ Hey Commander, just where~ are~ you~ staring~? Ahaha~♡
303181.name: Fancy Waves

305113.desc: Even I like to dress down and unwind from time to time. Oh? This is new and exciting for you? Well, you are welcome to come see more of it from now on! Hahaha!
305113.name: Reverence for Rest and Relaxation

9707010.desc: I'm getting all fired up! The name's Hiryuu, Hiryuu from the 2nd CarDiv. As a member of this fleet, I'll obey your orders. I do hope that you are qualified to lead us.
9707010.name: Hiryuu META

201233.desc: Commander, thou promised to go to the festival with me, right? If thou forgot, I shall have to give thee a nibble upon the neck, ehehe~
201233.name: Night Princess's Regalia

201109.desc: This outfit is a little tight... Yes, really? I understand. I've got to work harder for the Royal Navy!
201109.name: Cygnet (Retrofit)

303180.desc: Mogami-class heavy cruiser number four – Kumano.
303180.name: Kumano

305112.desc: It's about time for the flowers to bloom once more. Alas, how the time flies by... Ahem, Commander, let's see, would you like to go blossom-viewing with me?
305112.name: Blossom-Viewing Season

802021.desc: "O chosen hero, I bestow this sword upon you so that you may clear any obstacles in your path..." Commander, how did that sound?
802021.name: Saintess of the Sea

301143.desc: Commander, look at me, look at me! What do you think of my new outfit? If you like it, wanna give it a feel?
301143.name: Carnivore Carnival!

201234.desc: Feast thine eyes upon Vampire's idol attire... is it not exquisite? Heheh, now thy gaze shall be fixed upon my performance alone~♪
201234.name: Night Princess Idol

201110.desc: F-class destroyer ー Foxhound, Hull Number H69!
201110.name: Foxhound

9707030.desc: I am Souryuu of the Sakura Empire's 2nd CarDiv. Let's skip the formalities and get to work right away.
9707030.name: Souryuu META

303128.desc: Commander... Ahh, from now on, shouldn't I call you "darling?" Come and hold my hand... Ah, at times like these, I just can't help but to want to eat you up, dar~ling~
303128.name: Lily-White Vow

206060.desc: Colossus-class light aircraft carrier – Perseus (HMS Perseus.)
206060.name: Perseus

203081.desc: Cheers, Commander. I'm glad that the party is a success. Well, I should take care as well to not sully the honour of the royal family with my actions.
203081.name: A Glorious Toast

303123.desc: Student handbook, textbooks... twin guns, torpedoes... and what else... Huh? Commander, I'm just packing my bags for school... is there anything I'm missing?
303123.name: School Traumerei

302200.desc: Agano-class light cruiser number one – Agano.
302200.name: Agano

105100.desc: Colorado class battleship— Maryland, hull number BB-46
105100.name: Maryland

303122.desc: Oh my, it's begun to snow. Commander, should we find a nice, quiet place to enjoy the view?
303122.name: Hallmarks of Winter

302201.desc: Even though I'm not really into this whole "Christmas" thing, if it means I get to toy around with your heart by wearing this cute outfit of mine, then I suppose I would be interested. Hehe~
302201.name: Christmas Eve Tease

102060.desc: Atlanta-class light cruiser – Atlanta, Hull Number CL-51!
102060.name: Atlanta

10700031.desc: Blowing bubbles while sitting on a swing... It might seem a bit childish, but there's nothing wrong with enjoying activities like these every so often.
10700031.name: A Little Evening Secret

319011.desc: Ack... Owww... My apologies, Commander, I seem to have slipped on something... At times, it's hard to notice things I'm about to step on... Ugh...
319011.name: Hot Springs Relaxation

10700021.desc: Oh, the fireworks display is starting. I'm planning to meet up with the others after this, but... Why don't we spend some time enjoying the view here first?
10700021.name: Reflections of Heavenly Flowers

102130.desc: Brooklyn-class Light Cruiser – St. Louis, Hull Number CL-49!
102130.name: St. Louis

202229.desc: I am now more capable than ever of demonstrating the Royal Maids' style. Though I am not as talented as my sister, Curacoa, I sincerely hope you will find my service satisfactory. It is a great honour to work for you.
202229.name: Curlew (Retrofit)

303124.desc: So, you want big sister to be your "fleet queen"? You got it. But you'd better give it your all out there, or else I'll be upset with you!
303124.name: Stunning Speedster

305118.desc: I, battleship Mikasa, from now until eternity, pledge to you my undying love and devotion. May we help each other, encourage each other, and walk side-by-side on the same path. I hope to meet your expectations, as unworthy as I may be.
305118.name: Untarnished Splendor

102262.desc: "Superhero spin-off! The superhero who saved the world is enjoying a hard-earned vacation on the afternoon beach with the sidekick!" ... Hehe, Commander, a tagline like that sounds pretty cool, doesn't it?
102262.name: Summer Spin-off

10700061.desc: Summer's all about the festivals, and Ami Futami's the queen of festivals! Even the fireworks soaring through the sky can't hold a candle to how brilliant Ami is, so keep your eyes on me, Commander~♪
10700061.name: Summer Flowers and Sizzling Beats

701050.desc: How do you like my outfit, dear comrade? ...Is that so? After all of Tashkent's work to become an idol, that's how you react? Hmph. Just you wait. My next concert will rock your socks off.
701050.name: Tashkent μ

10700041.desc: Listening to the wind flow through the chimes on the porch seems to carry the summer heat right away. Commander, would you also like to come unwind with me?
10700041.name: Midsummer Relaxation

101471.desc: Zzz... Commander? S-sorry, I fell asleep for a bit... Uh, umm, what would you like me to do...?
101471.name: Sleeping Bunny

301141.desc: Come out of your office, Commander! You'll become lazy if you huddle up next to the heater all day! Let's go out and play in the snow!
301141.name: Shogun of Snowballs

107019.desc: Listen carefully or I'll step on you!
107019.name: Langley (Retrofit)

202230.desc: I am Swiftsure, a light cruiser of the Royal Navy... If it is not too much for one such as myself to ask, I would like to support your fleet in whatever way I can.
202230.name: Swiftsure

205070.desc: King George V-class battleship - HMS Duke of York.
205070.name: Duke of York

105171.desc: One, two, jump! Woah, think I nailed it this time~♪ So, how many points would you give me for that? Naturally, a perfect 100, right? Don'tcha just love it when things go smoothly?
105171.name: Exhilarating Steps!

301151.desc: Stupid Commander, I'm not a damn submarine! Do you wanna get hit in the face with an oxygen torpedo?
301151.name: Attack, I-490!

201238.desc: Those who fall in love with vampires are bound to suffer seven times more than their infatuation. After all, love is a poison which leads to death.
201238.name: Eloi's Blessing

102131.desc: What do you think of this foreign dress, Commander? *Giggle* ...Perhaps it's rekindled something within you?
102131.name: Blue and White Pottery

202231.desc: Commander, why are you here...? Me? Yes, as you can see, I'm still studying... I figured that acquiring knowledge would be the best way to make up for my lack of experience on the actual battlefield.
202231.name: Study Hall Cyclamen

102263.desc: Come on in, Commander! Don't you recognize me? I'm Reno Bunnino – cutesy bunny girl by day, villain-vanquishing superhero by night! Pretty neat concept, am I right?
102263.name: Reno Bunnino

301152.desc: Oh my. Commander, you must be pretty lucky to bump into me here, hehe~ Since you're here, you can have the privilege of being my escort tonight. Now, be grateful~♪
301152.name: The Ballroom's Lucky Star

101270.desc: Benson-class Destroyer - Bailey, Hull Number DD-492!
101270.name: Bailey

201099.desc: Cute? Pretty? Is that all? Can't you expand your vocabulary a little? Jeez... Commander, you really should learn to whisper sweet nothings into my ear!
201099.name: Crescent (Retrofit)

107080.desc: Wasp-class aircraft carrier, Wasp. Hull Number CV-7.
107080.name: Wasp

202232.desc: I agreed to try on this outfit, but... I know these fancy outfits don't suit me... H-huh, I look gorgeous?! ...Thank you very much. Even if you're just trying to make me feel better, I appreciate it...
202232.name: Beauty of White Jade

303130.desc: Third ship of the {namecode:66}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:68}.
303130.name: Maya

205072.desc: Ahh, this luscious scent... comes from thee. What dost thee feel when gazing upon my new dress? Hehe... your lips may lie but your eyes do not...
205072.name: Eternal Night's Carola

201100.desc: C-class destroyer ー Cygnet, Hull Number H83!
201100.name: Cygnet

302202.desc: "Oh my, you're also out for a stroll? Hehe, my name's Agano. And what might yours be?" ...Jeez, Commander, take this more seriously. According to the setting, we just met for the first time.
302202.name: Dating Game?

201240.desc: J-class destroyer – Jupiter, Hull Number F85.
201240.name: Jupiter

302203.desc: The blunt approach is not my style, but I cannot have Noshiro think I only inch my way to success... Oh, I was just talking to myself, Commander. Hehe, so anyway, would you mind being my partner for tonight's party?
302203.name: Blue Butterfly's Confession

301148.desc: Commander, look! Look at this new dress. Red and white, I really really like it! But what's the occasion?
301148.name: The Bride of Solomon

101271.desc: Can you see the ghost next to me? Hehehe— the black witch from Planet Bunny is none other than me, Bailey!
101271.name: Trickster Black Rabbit

201101.desc: Well, the swimsuit that Hood gave to me is a little tight, don't you think? Want to play beach volleyball? Do you think... can we win?
201101.name: Sea Star on Shore

702022.desc: Mmmh~ I sure could get used to this life~ Oh, Commander, thanks for being my gofer~♪ Ah, you can leave the cherries right over here!
702022.name: Sweet Cherry Memories

403010.desc: Admiral Hipper-class Heavy Cruiser, Admiral Hipper
403010.name: Admiral Hipper

201102.desc: H-happy Christmas! A-after that... umm... I have this present for ya, Commander...
201102.name: Holy Night's Hymn

202219.desc: It is my honour to be of everyone's service. Light cruiser Curacoa takes it upon herself to continue serving you, Master.
202219.name: Curacoa (Retrofit)

205090.desc: King George V-class battleship – Howe (HMS Howe.)
205090.name: Howe

101070.desc: Gridley-class destroyer - McCall, Hull Number DD-400!
101070.name: McCall

301159.desc: Heheh~ Retrofitting the mighty Shigure proves that you are quite perceptive! Aren't you glad that you get to rely on me more, you lucky idiot of a commander~♪
301159.name: Shigure (Retrofit)

701031.desc: You've violated the Minsk Protocol, comrade! Therefore, the sentence appropriate for you is imprisonment! Until when? Obviously, until your jailor is satisfied~♪
701031.name: Thunderous Jailor

101264.desc: Eldridge and kitties, idol mode... Commander, you like...?
101264.name: Kitty Idol

701042.desc: Urrk... Who dares disturb Tashkent's slumber? ...Oh, it's you, dear comrade? Um, in that case... I can always get more rest later. Is something the matter?
701042.name: The Blue Snoozer

213020.desc: Erebus-class monitor – Terror, Hull Number I03!
213020.name: Terror

701041.desc: ...*Sigh*, I never thought I'd get captured by these little guys... Dear comrade, does Tashkent really have to play along with this?
701041.name: The Bound Cruiser

103250.desc: The name's Baltimore, Eagle Union heavy cruiser. Whoops, right, I'm not just a soldier anymore, but an idol as well. I agreed to do it, and I'm gonna do it as best I can. We'll be counting on your support, Commander.
103250.name: Baltimore μ

301161.desc: Wa ha ha! My "universal-as-long-as-there-is-a-ceiling" swing set is finally complete! Commander, are you jealous? Want to give it a try? Too~ bad~! This seat is reserved only for the noble and elegant Yukikaze!
301161.name: Sovereign of the Swing

702029.desc: My retrofitting is done! Look forward to seeing how both my cuteness and combat potential have been upgraded!
702029.name: Pamiat‘ Merkuria (Retrofit)

601021.desc: Lady Veneto advised me to enjoy my time off by changing into something befitting the occasion... Um, Commander, I d-don't look strange, do I?
601021.name: Refreshing Sundress

702032.desc: Phew... Oh my, Commander, I'm sorry I didn't welcome you at the door. You don't have to be so tense - I already know not to try doing anything weird with you. Hehe~
702032.name: White Cavalier's Respite

201104.desc: M-Master... good evening... C-Commander, don't stare at me so intently... *Whimper*... Saratoga told me that this is part of marketing yourself as an idol...
201104.name: An Offer To Be Maid

202221.desc: You can feel the profound heritage and culture of the Dragon Empery from all these customs and outfits for the Lunar New Year's Festival… It seems to be ever more necessary to study the traditions and etiquette of this wondrous culture.
202221.name: Rhythm of the Dragon Empery

302210.desc: Agano-class light cruiser number two – Noshiro.
302210.name: Noshiro

<color=#fad545>Can be built after unlocking</color>
402040.name: Leipzig

101254.desc: I-I'm nobody's surprise! Ugh, I should've never listened to Sims... Stop staring already and undo these ribbons around my arms!
101254.name: Holy Night Surprise!

202122.desc: This is special cold-weather equipment inspired by Eagle Union designs. It was made for practical purposes such as special operations in frigid climates, and as such, was not designed with appearances in mind. Please do forgive me, Master.
202122.name: Serene Steel

401235.desc: Hi, welcome! How may I serve y– It's you, Commander?! Err, well, I'm working as a trainee at this Sakura Empire-style café, you see... What do you think of this outfit?
401235.name: Café Trainee @New Base

107064.desc: There is no doubt in my mind that I was born to fight. For the azure lanes of liberty, Enterprise, engaging!
107064.name: Soaring Wings of Freedom

10500070.desc: Good Miovening! I'm Ookami Mio. Over here, I seem to be... some sort of aircraft carrier. Let's get along well.
10500070.name: Ookami Mio

205102.desc: Why the astonished look on your face? You heard me correctly! On this day, I am not merely Valiant, I am the regal and royal Queen Valiant!
205102.name: Queen Valiant I

401236.desc: Jeez... Javelin's got what it takes, but I'm really concerned about Laffey and Ayanami. Oh well, I guess it's up to me to manage them... Commander, please don't forget to support me too.
401236.name: Serious Idol @Acting Manager?!

202123.desc: Good evening. The Royal Maids will be chaperoning this event. It is my hope to prevent any inappropriate behaviour that might interfere with the enjoyment of the attendees. Please pardon any inconveniences this may cause.
202123.name: The Noble Attendant

401237.desc: Commander, please help hold onto the ladder. I've almost got the book... Just a little more... All right... C-Commander?! Please don't look up!
401237.name: The Eyecatch in the Rye?

102240.desc: Light cruiser Cleveland, right here! I'm new to this whole idol biz, but I'll go with the flow and give it my all! Oh, and I'm counting on your support, Commander!
102240.name: Cleveland μ

205101.desc: Hehe~ As this medical facility training is crucially important, a charismatic leader such as myself would be best suited to instruct everyone on– Wait a moment, what's with this outfit?! You there, explain the meaning of this at once!
205101.name: Mischievous Little Nurse

401238.desc: Whew... Sorry to keep you waiting. I was having a hard time deciding which outfit to wear... Ah, um... how do I look?
401238.name: Schwarze Hochzeit

106010.desc: Long Island-class escort carrier – Long Island, Hull Number CVE-1!
106010.name: Long Island

202124.desc: Hehe~ Judging from your expression, Master, my outfit has not fallen short of your expectations. As time is precious, allow me to serve you to the utmost on this "date."
202124.name: Shopping with the Head Maid

401239.desc: My efficiency should be upgraded along with my performance. Paperwork, battle plans... I can handle them all! Commander, be prepared, we’ll be very busy~
401239.name: Z23 (Retrofit)

202125.desc: Welcome, table for one? Of course, right this way. Oh? What is it? Ah... I'm filling in for the manager at the moment, so that makes you my customer rather than my master, no?
202125.name: Piping-Hot Perfection

401241.desc: Come, human! The rite of festivities is upon us! Come hither, and let us revel in this foreign holiday together!
401241.name: Festival-going Fiend

199022.desc: Heh heh, the warm sun and the sea breeze really hit the spot, don't they? Alright, let's get out there and enjoy ourselves! That's what you've been waiting for, right, Commander?
199022.name: Lanier Swan

402049.desc: I feel like Fishy is a lot more capable than before, but I don't feel much different... M-maybe Fishy was the one to get a retrofit instead of me?!
402049.name: Leipzig (Retrofit)

301212.desc: C-Commander, I will be your partner for the party tonight. Let's see, umm... I believe this is proper Royal Navy etiquette... D-did I do it correctly?
301212.name: Hatsuharu in the Limelight

302019.desc: I've finally finished developing my new equipment! Since we still have time, let's go and try it out in live combat right now, Master!
302019.name: Yuubari (Retrofit)

106011.desc: Everyone's favorite and talked-about Long Island, actually has another hidden secret...
106011.name: Long Island - Indoor Slacker

105080.desc: Tennessee-class battleship – California, Hull Number BB-44!
105080.name: California

202250.desc: I am Sheffield, from the Royal Maids. I will explain how this transpired to you, so please stop looking like the world has turned upside down.
202250.name: Sheffield μ

202126.desc: It took me quite some time to prepare a suitable traditional Sakura Empire outfit. Terribly sorry. Master, won't you please allow this Belfast to serve you for another year?
202126.name: Folded Fascination

199023.desc: Happy New Year, Commander! I guess you dress up all flashy like this for the Sakura New Year. Would you escort me...? What are you gawking like that for...? Haha, am I so dazzling? Hahaha!
199023.name: Exalted Vibrance

502051.desc: Happy New Year, Commander! This red envelope is my gift to you... after all, that's my responsibility as a big sister! Anyway, hurry up and take it!
502051.name: Plum Blossom's Illumination

502050.desc: Chao Ho-class protected cruiser – Chao Ho.
502050.name: Chao Ho

301471.desc: What's the matter, Commander? Oh, this outfit? ...Um, I heard that this outfit would bring you therapeutic benefits and hoped to try it on... Wh-what do you think? Does it feel therapeutic to you?
301471.name: Soft and Fluffy Therapy

101249.desc: Y'know, Commander~ No matter how nice you are to me, I'm still going to prank you~ Oh, but if you want my help with pranking others, I'll consider it~ Heehee~
101249.name: Sims (Retrofit)

301720.desc: Special Type I-class destroyer number 10 – Uranami.
301720.name: Uranami

101451.desc: Welcome, Commander! I would fetch you our menu, but I've had a teensy accident here... Don't worry, I'll fix this somehow!
101451.name: Charming Rabbit

202019.desc: Everything as you wish, Commander. Oh? Yes, I'm Leander!
202019.name: Leander (Retrofit)

101319.desc: Commander, what month is it...? I think I overslept a bit... am I taller than I was before? *Yawn*... Gotta be because I slept the whole time...
101319.name: Nicholas (Retrofit)

301721.desc: It's snowing...! I've finished rallying the forces... so let us advance!
301721.name: Snow Vanguard

202128.desc: Are you destined for me? Greetings Belfast, from this moment onwards, I will always be with you.
202128.name: The Pledge of Claddagh

107990.desc: Yorktown-class aircraft carrier – Enterprise, Hull Number CV-6.
107990.name: Little Enterprise

304011.desc: We must fully live in the present, whether during work or during leisure - this is my mantra. Commander, shall we go for an outing together?
304011.name: The Beauties of Nature

207110.desc: I am the newest addition to the Muse System, Illustrious. Through my songs, I shall spread the light of love and peace— Don't you think that's a wonderful thing?
207110.name: Illustrious μ

404011.desc: A festival, huh? Going for days without fighting is boring, not to mention not my style. C'mon, Commander, isn't there *something* exciting I can do during this "Lunar New Year" festival?
404011.name: Panther und Pflaume

304010.desc: Kongou-class fast battleship number one – Kongou.
304010.name: Kongou

301219.desc: Hatsuharu, retrofit complete... H-hopefully I'm a little bit stronger now...
301219.name: Hatsuharu (Retrofit)

10500010.desc: We meet at last! I'm Hololive's virtual fox, Shirakami Fubuki! Commander, now that you've called me, we're gonna have a foxin' good time! Now then, let's get to work!
10500010.name: Shirakami Fubuki

101382.desc: While wearing clothes from the Dragon Empery, I can't help but reminisce about those days... Hehe, Commander, do you prefer me in Empery-style clothes, or Union-style clothes?
101382.name: Style of the East

101312.desc: Merry Christmas, Commander. I'm your present, probably... Would you mind closing the lid for me so I can sleep a bit more... zzz...
101312.name: Surprise!?

107060.desc: Yorktown-class aircraft carrier ー Enterprise, Hull Number CV-6!
107060.name: Enterprise

403080.desc: Heavy cruiser Roon, reporting for idol activities and associated experimental equipment testing. Today, we fight not with fire and sword, but with the power of song.
403080.name: Roon μ

201261.desc: Ah, Commander, over here! Hm, you're going to take care of all the plans for today's date? In that case, I look forward to seeing just how suave you can be! Hehe~
201261.name: Escort Me Please!

304012.desc: "Celebrity Endorsement of the Port Medical Facilities"... Hehehe, you've made a wise decision picking me. Commander, I can leave the ad shoot to you, right?
304012.name: Hospital Talent

201029.desc: Ardent told me I "gotta stop looking so tired" and I "gotta be more girly," so I did it while I was retrofitting... Do you recognise me, Commander? ... Umm, I'm Acasta, okay?
201029.name: Acasta (Retrofit)

303030.desc: First ship of the {namecode:55}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:55}.
303030.name: Aoba

301231.desc: Yaho~ Good morning, Commander! For a limited time only, Wakaba Claus will be delivering Christmas presents! Huh? My bag? Aaahhh! C-Commander, help me pick everything up!
301231.name: Holiday Special Wakaba!

101313.desc: Commander, did you also come to play in the pool? ...Me? Fletcher said I have to help clean up because I was slacking off... Mm, watch your step~
101313.name: Summer Cleaning "Volunteer"

101251.desc: I'm not really happy at all! But since you're bonding with me for once, I have to say... thank y... H-hmph! I didn't say anything!
101251.name: Rebellious Summer

201030.desc: A-class destroyer – Ardent, Hull Number H41.
201030.name: Ardent

107063.desc: Happy Anniversary! Commander, celebrate to your heart's content today! I'll be praying for our continued victories!
107063.name: Anniversary Ride

305011.desc: {namecode:79} said always dressing like a witch can be a bit old-fashioned, so she gave me a new outfit. That kid... Do you think it looks good on me, Commander?
305011.name: The Celebration of Spring

10600020.desc: Um... Are you the Commander? Oh, perfect! It's nice to meet you. My name is Honoka! I don't know how much I'll be able to help, but... let's be friends!
10600020.name: Honoka

10600010.desc: Hello! Oh... What am I supposed to call you? "Commander"? Got it! My name is Marie Rose. Just call me Marie, okay? I'm counting on your support, Commander!
10600010.name: Marie Rose

101050.desc: Gridley-class destroyer - Gridley, Hull Number DD-380!
101050.name: Gridley

10600050.desc: Are you the person who led Misaki to this port? You go by the name... "Commander"? Hmm... I don't know how you sweet-talked her into it, but you're not fooling me. The moment you do anything strange... you better be on guard! My name? It's Nagisa. You... silly dog!
10600050.name: Nagisa

103160.desc: Baltimore-class heavy cruiser – Baltimore, Hull Number CA-68.
103160.name: Baltimore

10600070.desc: Are you the one in charge here? The "Commander"? I'm Monica, the dealer! Well, dealer-in-training. I know it's sudden, but would you care to gamble with me? The stakes will, of course, be high!
10600070.name: Monica

502041.desc: Happy New Year, Commander. I've come to deliver you blessings for this coming year... Next, you're going to ask for a red envelope, right? Hehe, just teasing~
502041.name: Snowy Pine's Warmth

101314.desc: Commander, because you kept your promise and came... here's some chocolate, and a letter for you. Please read it later. No, it's not that big of a deal... Just a little embarrassing...
101314.name: After-School Promise

201032.desc: Welcome to Ardent's game house~! I'm here to provide fun and excitement for everyone as the GM– ...Ehehe, actually, I'm still learning as a play~♪
201032.name: Master Ardent?

401351.desc: Commander, and all my fellow friends of the fleet, Happy New Year's! This time, your favorite idol Z35 will be presenting a brand new Sakura-themed collaboration, "Projekt Kirschblüte!" Everyone, thank you for your continued support!
401351.name: Projekt Kirschblüte

407031.desc: Eugen, you said that this was is a ceremonial outfit from the Sakura Empire? Surprisingly, it does seem to suit me rather well. Oh, I'm supposed to offer my well-wishes for the New Year at this time, yes?
407031.name: Chronos's Kalendae

502040.desc: Chao Ho-class protected cruiser – Ying Swei.
502040.name: Ying Swei

900007.desc: King George V-class battleship, Prince of Wales. Hull Number 53.
900007.name: Prince of Wales

407030.desc: Graf Zeppelin-class aircraft carrier – Peter Strasser.
407030.name: Peter Strasser

305023.desc: Fusou told me that I have to wear a Western-style dress to the banquet, so she got one for me! Milord, Milord, isn't this dress pretty?
305023.name: Dressy Black Cat

202150.desc: Arethusa-class light cruiser - Aurora, pennant number 12
202150.name: Aurora

502034.desc: The Sakura Empire has lots of delicious food that I've never tried before! Yeah! It's a great place!
502034.name: Great Gourmet Expedition

305022.desc: Merry Christmas! Milord, milord, how do I look? Is my Christmas outfit pretty? Ehehe~ Big sis also praised me today!
305022.name: Holiday Offensive

101051.desc: Commander, Merry Christmas! Guhehe~ Won't you attend my "Super Special Sexy Sara (tentative)" photoshoot event?
101051.name: Christmas Photoshoot

407032.desc: You already know, don't you? Since I spent so much of my precious time changing into a dress for your sake... Heh, I'll be taking plenty of your time in return. Hehehe.
407032.name: A Moment Frozen in Pure White

305025.desc: Woah, even the air tastes totally different at this vacation spot! Milord, Milord, um, Akashi asked me to bottle up some of the air here for her! Want to give me a hand?
305025.name: Vacation Offensive!

202151.desc: I've been preparing for this day for quite some time... Commander, would you like to hear the book I wrote for you?
202151.name: The Tale of Spring

502036.desc: Cheese! That came out looking good! Hehehe~ I'm really glad to be a part of this charity event for nature, along with you and my sister! Baobao is really glad too!
502036.name: Baobao's Buddy!

305024.desc: Milord, Milord, welcome to the store! Yamashiro is a sales clerk today! Mhm, I'll do my best!
305024.name: Sales Clerk Offensive?!

303040.desc: Second ship of the {namecode:55}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:56}.
303040.name: Kinugasa

301054.desc: Compared to the way we celebrate New Year in the Sakura Empire, the festivities of the Dragon Empery have a completely different atmosphere... But, I don't really mind the liveliness... Commander, do you like festivals?
301054.name: Lunar Demon

805012.desc: Commander, I wish you a Happy New Year. May you avail yourself of the period of repose that follows the culmination of the year's duties. I pray that you and everyone else may receive the blessing of the Heavens.
805012.name: Evergreen Prophecy

201019.desc: Selecting me for a retrofit proves that you are a Commander of culture! Heheh, you'd better prepare yourself! From now on, I'll make sure to "take care" of you even more thoroughly!
201019.name: Amazon (Retrofit)

305019.desc: Milord! Thank you~ Not just for the retrofit, but for many many things. Hehe, it was the greatest of fortune for me and {namecode:79} to meet you.
305019.name: Fusou (Retrofit)

301055.desc: "Welcome, Commander..." I should greet customers like this... yes?
301055.name: Grade A Sailor Uniform

202152.desc: I've always believed that music is unique in its power to touch one's heart, so I decided to learn the violin. Commander, please enjoy my performance.
202152.name: Dawn's Paean

101176.desc: "Laffey came from Planet Bunny..." Umm, I forgot that line Benson told me to say... In any case, everyone, please give me lots of support... Actually, just a little support is fine... Uhh, I have to do it again with more motivation?
101176.name: Bunny Idol @Unmotivated

101440.desc: Allen M. Sumner-class destroyer – Cooper, Hull Number DD-695.
101440.name: Cooper

301056.desc: Ayanami here. Successfully infiltrated Commander's office. Oh... Commander saw me. Operation failed...
301056.name: Covert Ops Cloak

103030.desc: Northampton-class Heavy Cruiser – Northampton, Hull Number CA-26!
103030.name: Northampton

201020.desc: A-class destroyer – Acasta, Hull Number H09.
201020.name: Acasta

305021.desc: It’s just not summer without beach volleyball! Ah... Milord, you’re not playing? But I went through all this effort to pick out a swimsuit...
305021.name: Summer Offensive?

103162.desc: Heya, you here to watch the game? Heh, heavy cruiser Baltimore, the passerby solver of troubles, here to play it cool!
103162.name: Black Ace

105140.desc: South Dakota-class battleship – South Dakota, Hull Number BB-57!
105140.name: South Dakota

301057.desc: I guess I'm making my idol debut? Um, Javelin and the others are making their debuts, so, I also had to... Commander, what are idols supposed to do normally?
301057.name: Low-Key Idol @Confused

301050.desc: First ship of special Type II {namecode:6} class destroyers, {namecode:6}.
301050.name: Ayanami

102100.desc: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Columbia, hull number CL-56.
102100.name: Columbia

201021.desc: Hm? Guess we're both about to head out... Don't stare at me like that... Even I go outdoors sometimes... Since we're both, uh, headed the same way... maybe we could... walk there together?
201021.name: Fashionable Outing

102232.desc: Happy Lunar New Year, Commander. I'm trying out Dragon Empery fashion for a change, though this dress will some getting used to. Hey, uh, do you want to join me under the umbrella? For cover against the snowfall, I mean.
102232.name: Fruitful Snow of an Auspicious Year

101177.desc: Yaaawn... Laffey's cleaning her room, Commander... If you don't wanna help then just find a place to sit... Anyway, back to cleaning... Zzz...
101177.name: Sleep to Clean Another Day

101441.desc: 30 to 15... Next match will be mine, you hear! Oh, Commander, are you here to play a round of tennis?
101441.name: Blazing Tennis Battle

201022.desc: I heard you're supposed to hang lanterns up everywhere during the Spring Festival... so Ardent and I gave it a try! What do you think? Pretty cute, right? Um... I was talking about the lanterns...
201022.name: Lights of the Lantern Festival

103163.desc: Damn, that Bremerton... What did she make me wear this time... Even though I was the one to ask her for advice... Um... Ugh... This doesn't look too weird, right...?
103163.name: Evening Breeze Minuet

407011.desc: So the Second Movement is a Lento of the summer and the sea? So be it... Since we will arrive at the Finale eventually, I suppose I can enjoy this moment of fleeting peace with you.
407011.name: Beachside Urd

105141.desc: Massachusetts suggested I learn something useful that's unrelated to combat, so I started playing the piano... It seemed impossible at first, but after actually trying it, I've developed a pretty good feel for it.
105141.name: Solo Concert

108050.desc: Lights! Camera! Albacore! Ahaha, don't worry about it, I'm just getting fired up over here! Oh, did you come up with a better idea? Tell me, tell me~
108050.name: Albacore μ

102101.desc: Commander, here, I made some chocolate for you~ Come on, hurry up and take it already! Holding this pose makes me look like I'm waiting for some Prince Charming, and it's super embarrassing.
102101.name: After-School Odette

201023.desc: Come on, stop running around and behave already... Ah, Commander? Umm, I'm currently looking after these rabbits... Hm, you're thirsty? Um, give me a moment and I'll whip something up for you...
201023.name: Monochromatic Marvel

403070.desc: Huh? Why are you staring at me like I'm some weirdo? I'll have you know, it's not like I wanted to do this or anything!
403070.name: Admiral Hipper μ

101240.desc: Sims-class destroyer - Sims, Hull Number DD-409!
101240.name: Sims

305026.desc: Uwaah! M-Milord?! I'm so, so sorry... You didn't get hurt, did you? Um... This is my school uniform. Fusou tailored it for me, hehe~ ... Awawa! I should head off to class now! See you later!
305026.name: Street Corner Offensive!

101178.desc: Laffey seems to have changed a bit... Commander, do you like how Laffey is now?
101178.name: White Rabbit's Oath

101442.desc: Hm? I'm just wrapping up some presents! Can't just present them as-is, and all that. Hehe~ I could sure use a little help, Commander!
101442.name: Heartwarming Holiday Hearth

101310.desc: Fletcher-class destroyer – Nicholas, Hull Number DD-449!
101310.name: Nicholas

105010.desc: Nevada-class battleship – Nevada, Hull Number BB-36!
105010.name: Nevada

305029.desc: Milord! I can do anything now~ bombardment or aerial strikes! So, the thing is, you can totally count on me, much much more, Milord! Milord~!
305029.name: Yamashiro (Retrofit)

205012.desc: Now this is a stage worthy of our majesty! You are not to leave our sight, servant! Let your passions burn for me!
205012.name: One Night of the Queen

808012.desc: Mmmh~ Bonjour, Commander~ Nothing feels better than the waves lapping at your skin~ Oh, Commander, why don't you come lie down and experience it for yourself?
808012.name: Loisirs Balnéaires

403043.desc: I seem pleased? Of course I am. Why wouldn't I be when my sweet little sister will be joining us at the party? Now shape up and entertain your master, you lowly animal! Ahahahaha!
403043.name: Demon Princess' Dark Hour Banquet

305028.desc: Milord, Milord, I've finished changing! What do you think, what do you think? Milord, do you like Yamashiro's dress~?
305028.name: Bridal Attack!

301058.desc: This dress is... {namecode:6}’s. I'm not used to this dress yet... Commander, do you think it fits me?
301058.name: Demon's Finest Dress

403042.desc: One must not neglect sunscreen during the summer... Plebeian, if you wish to serve your master, prostrate yourself and yell "I beg of you, Queen Deutschland" three times, and I might consider giving you an opportunity. Ahahaha~
403042.name: Service Time?!

205011.desc: Hah haah! You're a lucky servant this evening! We shall allow you to accompany us to the party! ... B-but it's not like I chose you because I like you! I just... Yes! I just sort of chose randomly! Got it?!
205011.name: The Queen's Ball

301059.desc: Ayanami, retrofit complete. I feel stronger, yes... Having that said, Commander, can you pat my head? I want to be spoiled a bit...
301059.name: Ayanami (Retrofit)

901032.desc: Yes, the strings... I can hear the celebratory melody... Now, follow my lead and we'll take this song to greater– Oh, Commander? What's all this, you ask? Uhh... You know... Ahahaha...
901032.name: One-Girl Orchestra

101179.desc: Laffey, improved and reporting in! I feel energized and ready to redouble my efforts! Hey, Commander, I still don't want you to touch my ears...
101179.name: Laffey (Retrofit)

403044.desc: Why are so many people out and about during a holiday? ...That's it! Lowly animal, was it your idea to prepare all this to surprise me...?! Heh... Hehe, that's right, don't you dare disappoint me!
403044.name: Lantern-Lit Ruler

10100060.desc: I'm the CPU of Lastation, Black Heart. I've rushed here all the way from Gamindustri to lend you my aid. Be grateful.
10100060.name: Black Heart

301309.desc: Ohohoho, you must have a sharp eye if you've decided to retrofit me~ Now that I've been chosen, I cannot afford to embarrass you. Now, take a good and thorough look at this veteran's aspirations~
301309.name: Kamikaze (Retrofit)

205014.desc: Did I hear that you're supposed to give out red envelopes during the Dragon Empery's New Year? This is a fine chance to display the magnanimity of the Queen of the Royal Navy! ...Don't just run off with your gift! Spread the word of my glory, my servant!
205014.name: Crown Jewel of the Royal Navy

10100040.desc: My name is Vert, I am the CPU of Leanbox. I'm very good at first-person shooters, so please let me handle all combat-related matters!
10100040.name: Vert

10100050.desc: I am Purple Heart, the CPU of Planeptune. And you must be the commander. I will follow your orders from now.
10100050.name: Purple Heart

307018.desc: We should send out even more invites... This is the best way to rid ourselves of those pesky vixens all at once!
307018.name: Deep Crimson Poppy

101040.desc: Mahan-class destroyer - Downes, Hull Number DD-375!
101040.name: Downes

900133.desc: 北卡罗来纳级战列舰—北卡罗来纳，舷号BB-55
900133.name: North Carolina

307021.desc: "You only live once?" Where have I heard that saying before... Commander, are you getting excited?
307021.name: Everlasting Killing Stone

205013.desc: Hehe, behold the new outfit that I had Akashi make for me! Impressive, no? Prostrate yourself before the elegant charm of my school uniform, servant~♪
205013.name: Queen of the Campus

101110.desc: Fletcher-class destroyer - Charles Ausburne, Hull Number DD-570!
101110.name: Charles Ausburne

301319.desc: There we go... My fan is too big, and I'm not used to carrying it around yet... Ah, right, come here for a sec, Commander~ I'll fan you with some cool air~ Come on now, no need to be shy~
301319.name: Matsukaze (Retrofit)

331050.desc: Commander, Happy New Year's. In this coming year, please continue to look after me...
331050.name: Pulse of the New Year

10100020.desc: Are you the commander? Hmm... Very well. I'm Noire. The CPU of Lastation. You can put your mind at ease now that I'm here.
10100020.name: Noire

331051.desc: Commander, thank you for coming to the party. Ayanami... has been waiting for you. ...I look a bit scary? I'm not sure I get it... I guess.
331051.name: Nightfall Raiment

308022.desc: Commander, are you also waiting for the fireworks to start? There's still some time, so let's have a little chat!
308022.name: Shortly Before the Fireworks

301321.desc: Commander, Merry Christmas~! I am on my best behavior today as well! Uuu... when is Santa Claus going to come? I'm sleepy...
301321.name: Mr. Reindeer, Depart!

203030.desc: Kent-class heavy cruiser - Kent, Hull Number 54!
203030.name: Kent

403051.desc: I sailed alone, fought alone, and then I was sunk while being alone. Now I found a new beginning... Hmm? Commander, you've been staring and laughing at me since the beginning… do you want to eat this?
403051.name: Girl's Sunday

331052.desc: No, Ryuujou! Samurai builds should stay back during the boss! ...Oh, welcome, Commander. I'm busy with this game right now, so just make yourself at home or something.
331052.name: Off-Duty Battle Station Gear

202161.desc: Did I keep you waiting, Commander? Ahaha... A girl's gotta take her time before stepping out onto the streets, remember? Come on, take my hand, and let's get going! Hehe~
202161.name: Trendy and Vogue?

101041.desc: I heard another person was coming to help out at the store, but I never thought it'd be you, Commander! What am I doing here? Ahaha, well uh, I had a little bit of free time on my hands... right~♪
101041.name: Part-Time Bomber

403050.desc: Deutschland-class armored cruiser number three – Admiral Graf Spee.
403050.name: Admiral Graf Spee

112011.desc: Listen, everyone~! Playing by the beach is fun, but please keep safety in mind! If you begin to feel ill, come see me~!
112011.name: Revigorating Hestia

101173.desc: Have a happy and auspicious New Year? Uh.... can I go now...? I'm feeling a bit sleepy, so can I go back to sleep?
101173.name: White Rabbit Welcomes the Spring

703011.desc: What, you've never seen the inside of a shipgirl's room? It's not like you're here on official business, so stop standing around already. Find a place to sit and relax.
703011.name: Nostalgic Pilsner

301812.desc: Kasumi and Foo are excited about the new semester. Are you too, Commander?
301812.name: At School with Foo

403053.desc: It's so fancy, so formal... Is this a "party"? I'm not sure I'll be able to fit in... But if you'll go with me, Commander, I'll give it a try!
403053.name: A Novel Anniversary

10700010.desc: Hello, Commander! I'm the idol, Haruka Amami! I'll do my best to share my dreams with everyone in port! Let's all have a great time together!
10700010.name: Haruka Amami

10600021.desc: Whoa, the sea is so pretty~! It's as beautiful as the Venus Islands! I'm so blown away, I don't even feel the heat anymore!
10600021.name: Summer Angel on the Shore

408081.desc: Whenever I play games with Bulldog, I always end up losing. Frustratinggg. That's why... I'll study hard. One day, I'll winnnn.
408081.name: Kleiner Hai

403052.desc: I never dreamt that I'd be able to don this outfit and live a normal, peaceful life... Thank you, Commander...
403052.name: Peaceful Daily Life

301014.desc: The whole world's going to feel the tremors from my debut! I'm Fubuki, the Special-type idol!
301014.name: Fubuki Halation!

10700020.desc: Pleased to meet you. My name is Chihaya Kisaragi. Are you the one in charge of this port? I look forward to working with you.
10700020.name: Chihaya Kisaragi

202271.desc: My, what brings you here, Commander? Are you feeling unwell? That's no good... Why don't you come sit over here first? I'll start by taking your temperature...
202271.name: Pure White Angel

307023.desc: This statue seems to have been inspired by the teachings of the Iris Orthodoxy. Though I am unfamiliar with this kind of art, gazing upon such majesty... fills one with a sense of piety. Commander, can you feel it as well?
307023.name: Exalted White Wings

107381.desc: Commander, welcome to my "Utopia." Here, you can find my prized collection. Now, where should we start our detailed tour?
107381.name: Utopia's Collector

408080.desc: Raaaawr. U-110 is a shaaaark. Fear meeee. Mess with me and I'll bite yooouuu.
408080.name: U-110

408051.desc: It's time for science class with U-73! Now, Commander, let's try out an exhilarating and positively fascinating experiment!
408051.name: Science Rules!

302070.desc: Nagara-class light cruiser number four – Yura.
302070.name: Yura

301015.desc: Welcome, welcome! Oh, Commander! I've actually started working here part-time, but I'm still learning— Wooah?! Phew... Th-that was a close one...
301015.name: Stormy Waitress-in-Training!

10600061.desc: Oho! To think there was a place with this much class... Not bad! I shall hereby be enjoying my hot springs vacation right here, hehehe.
10600061.name: Scarlet-Tinged Hot Spring Vacation

201232.desc: Commander, I am now a nurse, so thou hast no choice but to give me thy blood~! Hehe, just kidding~!
201232.name: Little Devil in White

499011.desc: Such a delightful party with our wonderful friends in this peaceful harbor... It's wonderful, really... But, it's all so boring...
499011.name: Dark Red Grin

202039.desc: I'll allow you to lick my feet since I'm in such a good mood today. What? I can't believe you'd turn down such a great opportunity!
202039.name: Ajax (Retrofit)

408050.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIB submarine – U-73.
408050.name: U-73

112010.desc: Repair ship ー Vestal, Hull Number AR-4!
112010.name: Vestal

403054.desc: My sister just wouldn't stop bugging me, so I finally caved and agreed to do this... Anyways, all I have to do is get up on stage and sing, right?
403054.name: World's♥Cutest

103020.desc: Pensacola-class Heavy Cruiser – Salt Lake City, Hull Number CA-25!
103020.name: Salt Lake City

405011.desc: My sincerest apologies for the delay, Commander. Ah, excuse me... as the fleet leader of the Iron Blood, I'm expected to wear this outfit to various formal occasions. Just putting it on seems to make me inadvertently change the way I speak...
405011.name: Beacon of the Iron Blood

101174.desc: I'm done changing... how is it? Today, I’m supposed to call you “valued guest?” Um... I don’t really get it...
101174.name: Bunny Clerk?

10700011.desc: Good evening, Commander! Are you also taking a break? If so, let's go get some candied apples and have a little chat~♪
10700011.name: A Taste of Tranquility

307013.desc: Commander, I've been waiting for you~ What a sinful one you are, to tempt Akagi like this for so long... But at long last, nobody will ever get between us again...♡
307013.name: Ruby-Laced Beauty

103090.desc: New Orleans-class heavy cruiser – Quincy, hull number CA-39.
103090.name: Quincy

399012.desc: This is my first time wearing Western clothes... Um, Milord! Does this outfit... suit Ibuki well...?
399012.name: Snow on the Wind

299031.desc: Cheer up, Owner! Jeez, why are you so bummed out when we're at the beach... Because it's just a normal playdate instead of a romantic date? What's the difference anyway? C'mon, let's go head down to where the others are~!
299031.name: Summery Date!

10700051.desc: Sorry, what? A paddle showdown? Commander, please... You play that in a kimono, not a yutaka. But if you insist... If I win, you're buying me an ice cream!
10700051.name: Paddle Showdown - Summer Formation

301350.desc: The fourth ship of {namecode:33} class destroyer — {namecode:137}
301350.name: Uzuki

299022.desc: So, an Eastern outfit this time... Hmph. My nobility is evident regardless of what I wear. However, since you prepared this outfit especially for me, it would be unbecoming of me to not express my gratitude. Thank you.
299022.name: Black Gerard

10600051.desc: Whew! The wind feels great! ...What are you staring at me like that for, you silly dog? You're the one who said you wanted to go to the beach, remember? To start with, how about... we take a stroll?
10600051.name: Blue Skies, Good Vibes

299032.desc: I'll sing a song for you, Owner~ Ahem... Wait, I'm not sure I know any Dragon Empery songs, actually...
299032.name: Cait Sith Crooner

304050.desc: 1st Ship of the Amagi-class Battlecruisers, Amagi
304050.name: Amagi

10700071.desc: Woah~! They're starting to send up the huge fireworks! ...Hey, Commander, just where are you looking? Did Mami's alluring yukata make you go crazy with desire~?
10700071.name: Alluring Festival

301329.desc: Comainder, I'm done retrofitting! Have some candy! Hm? You're always nice to me, so I'm giving you some candy!
301329.name: Mutsuki (Retrofit)

10600011.desc: Hmm, this swimsuit is pretty cute, but isn't it a bit childish? ...In any case, if you like it, then it's all good!
10600011.name: Devilish Servant Against the Splashing Waves

301011.desc: Oh no! I-I'm gonna be late for school! Y-you need to speed up too, doggy! *Pant*... *pant*... Why'd none of my sisters wake me up before they left?!
301011.name: 5 Minutes Till I'm Late

899011.desc: With all due respect, Commander, this finery and this throne are not fit for one such as myself. Despite the hallowed name I have inherited, I am nothing more than a warrior. —However, if such an arrangement pleases you, then I shall hold my objections.
899011.name: Holy Knight's Resplendence

102160.desc: Omaha-class light cruiser – Memphis, Hull Number CL-12.
102160.name: Memphis

102098.desc: Man, this is so embarrassing... C-Commander, w-w-what do you, umm, like, think of my d-d-d-dress...?
102098.name: Heartfelt Moment

301322.desc: Comainder, I put on my yukata just like you said! Ehehe, you should take me to the festival so I can get lots and lots of candy!
301322.name: Candy Festival!

899012.desc: Commander, regarding your next appointment... Ah, hard work is one of the highest virtues of the Iris's holy knights. On weekdays or vacations, in knights' armor or the Dragon Empery's attire, there can be no pause to my prayer, my training, or my duties as the administrator of your will.
899012.name: Alluring Administrator

399041.desc: Commander? Oh, I haven't quite finished changing. My hair still needs work... Sorry, would you mind waiting a bit longer?
399041.name: Soft Voice of Spring

301012.desc: "C-come on in! We've got special offers for you!" ... W-wait, is this really what a "sexy mascot" would wear? It feels pretty different from what I was expecting... And boy, is it stuffy in this thing...
301012.name: Mascot Bucky

203019.desc: Um... Your Excellency, could you please stop staring at me like you don't recognise me? I didn't think that I'd get a new look for my retrofit, either... But, don't you think it's rather cute?
203019.name: London (Retrofit)

301571.desc: Happy New Year, Commander! I am currently on my way to give a Kagura dance at the shrine. If you have time... would you like to come see it?
301571.name: A Dance for the Coming Spring

299033.desc: "Owner~ I've come to take you to the ball~" ...That's exactly what you were going to do? Eh, doesn't matter who does it~ All that matters is we'll be there together~♪
299033.name: The Cat and the White Steed

301323.desc: I heard that if I go around telling people "Happy New Year," I can get lots of goodies! Ehehe, I hope they'll give me a bunch of candy!
301323.name: Spring Festival Sweets

103091.desc: Everyone's so cheerful and energetic... Commander, um, if you're tired, want to rest here with me?
103091.name: Sizzling Summer, Brisk Breeze

108040.desc: Gato-class submarine – Bluegill, Hull Number SS-242.
108040.name: Bluegill

899021.desc: It is not against the teachings to halt one's pursuit of destiny and to surrender to the warm draft of festivities. It is mankind's prerogative to seek out auspicious portents.
899021.name: Lapis Lazuli's First Dream

203020.desc: London-class heavy cruiser – Shropshire, Hull Number 73!
203020.name: Shropshire

403031.desc: Relaxing on a float, gently licking my lips... is this really the most popular photo pose for the beach? Wales, you’re not teasing me again, are you?
403031.name: Unfading Smile

10600060.desc: Oh? You don't seem to fear me... Who might you be? ...I see, so it is you who rules over this place. Then I shall call you "Commander." I am Nyotengu. You would do best to keep me entertained, hehe.
10600060.name: Nyotengu

10600040.desc: It's nice to meet you! From what I've heard, you're the "Commander," right? I'm Misaki. I have experience with various part-time jobs, so... I'm confident that I can be of help to you all. Let's do our best!
10600040.name: Misaki

10600030.desc: Are you the Owner of the port? The "Commander"? Hello. My name is Kasumi, I'll be staying here for the foreseeable future. I hope we can both get along on friendly terms.
10600030.name: Kasumi

207052.desc: Yes, this will do wonderfully! Thank you, ladies. Phew... Getting dressed is so dreadfully time-consuming... Ahem! How silly of me. I must not whine in the presence of others.
207052.name: Timeless Classics

10700030.desc: Hello, hello~! My name is Iori Minase! It's such a pleasure to meet you! ...Huh? There's no need for me to force myself...? Hey, wait a second, what do you mean by that?!
10700030.name: Iori Minase

199021.desc: Oh? Commander, did you need to get some fresh air as well? Me? Ahaha... It's a bit too stiff inside that venue, so I came out for a change of pace. Why don't we take a little stroll together?
199021.name: South Town Pearl

403030.desc: Admiral Hipper-class Heavy Cruiser, Prinz Eugen
403030.name: Prinz Eugen

202291.desc: Aurora chose this outfit for me because... the Spring Festival represents a time of celebration in the Dragon Empery, and red is the color that best symbolizes that. What do you think? Does this outfit... make you feel more festive?
202291.name: Ruby-Red Boudoir

199013.desc: Supportive sorceress Seattle, comin' in hot! So, something got you down, my good pal? I'm up to talk about whatever's on your mind, but in return, you've gotta come to my party tonight!
199013.name: Sunfish Spell!

10700070.desc: Nihihi~♪ I'm the idol, Mami Futami! You'll get to feast your eyes on how alluring Mami is, so look forward to it, Commander~!
10700070.name: Mami Futami

102231.desc: Good morning, Commander. Unfortunately, this bicycle only seats one person, but I could dismount and lead it along as we walk together.
102231.name: Rider of Red

101300.desc: Fletcher-class destroyer - Jenkins, Hull Number DD-447!
101300.name: Jenkins

403033.desc: ... Huh? Commander, is that you? Me, drunk? No way... *hic*... If I was, Commander, then what are you planning to do to me? Hehe...
403033.name: Cordial Cornflower

301831.desc: Akashi pushed me into getting this outfit, saying that it would surely make you happy, but... What do you think...?
301831.name: Long Waves of Happiness

299041.desc: Phew... Swimming like this doesn't feel all that refreshing... Hey, how about you stop staring and come join me?
299041.name: The Golden Hind's Respite

101370.desc: Benson class Destroyer— Kalk, hull number DD-611.
101370.name: Kalk

408061.desc: Commander, welcome to the school band! Why'd I join the band? The reason's simple - there's no Motorbike Club at school, haha! Just kidding~! Actually, I'm quite fond of music as well, heh.
408061.name: Ironbrass Trombonist

403032.desc: So this is the Sakura Empire's New Year? Hehe, how interesting~ Commander, since it's the New Year, why don't you put aside all those papers and have a drink with me?
403032.name: Profusion of Flowers

105070.desc: Tennessee-class battleship – Tennessee, Hull Number BB-43!
105070.name: Tennessee

301832.desc: There's still some time before the banquet begins, and I'm afraid I'm feeling a little sleepy... W-would you mind if I took a nap? Thank you...
301832.name: Long-Awaited Warmth

10500071.desc: I changed into my swimsuit, but I wonder if it looks right on me? An outfit like this might make you feel breezier just by looking at it~
10500071.name: Summer Vacation

999011.desc: Gascogne uniform change complete. Directive assigned: have fun on the beach with Master. Requesting detailed instructions for how to "have fun on the beach."
999011.name: Tropical Environs Acclimation Service Equipment

10700040.desc: Why hello, my name's Azusa Miura~ Um, this is a port, right? And these are... shipgirls? Um~ Where exactly am I?
10700040.name: Azusa Miura

408060.desc: Iron Blood Type VIIC submarine – U-101.
408060.name: U-101

302081.desc: Grr! What are you here for? Speak up. ...Oh, you just wanted to take a tour of the club activities? Sorry 'bout that, I don't like getting disturbed in the middle of this kind of training.
302081.name: New Year's Blade Demon

10700050.desc: Pleased to meet you. My name is Ritsuko Akizuki. I was wondering what was going to happen to me when I suddenly got blown away, but... In any case, I'm pleased to make your acquaintance!
10700050.name: Ritsuko Akizuki

10700060.desc: Nihihi! I'm the idol, Ami Futami! This place seems awfully lively, just perfect for pranking~! See you around, Commander!
10700060.name: Ami Futami

207010.desc: Eagle-class light aircraft carrier – Eagle (HMS Eagle.)
207010.name: Eagle

102092.desc: Why am I stuck with this tuxedo when everyone else is wearing a dress?! ... Though it does feel slick, so I guess it's pretty nice. So, weren't we gonna go to the party, Commander? Then it's about time we head out!
102092.name: Gentry Knight

405021.desc: Summer... In the past, it was always just a hot and stifling season... But now...? Doesn't my outfit tell the whole story? Let's get going, there's bound to be a lot of people on the beach.
405021.name: Snow-Melting Summer

102030.desc: Brooklyn-class Light Cruiser – Brooklyn, Hull Number CL-40!
102030.name: Brooklyn

202029.desc: The cute and charming Achilles is Super☆Retro☆Fitted! Even my heel won't give me any problems now! Well, not like it really ever did before, ahaha~☆
202029.name: Achilles (Retrofit)

207029.desc: Ark Royal retrofitting complete! Now I can protect you, my friends, and of course, the little destroyers, to the very end!
207029.name: Ark Royal (Retrofit)

101450.desc: I'm Eagle Union destroyer Allen M. Sumner! Just call me Allen! It's a pleasure, Commander! Anyway, I've heard you've got yummy food and cushy work here at this port. That true?
101450.name: Allen M. Sumner

102162.desc: We have to work hard if we want to play hard, isn't that right, Commander? Are you ready for our happy Halloween?
102162.name: Mystical Night

308041.desc: Hi there, Commander. Oh, this outfit? I'll be wearing it to school today. By the way, did you want to come sit in on my class?
308041.name: Coral Reef Bunny

206061.desc: I'm Perseus, I will be your nurse today. Use this button to call for me if you need anything... Yes? Did you need something?
206061.name: Unfamiliar Duties

900300.desc: 您好！那个…应该怎么称呼您呢？“指挥官”？我明白了！我是玛莉萝丝，叫我玛莉就可以了！请多指教，指挥官先生！
900300.name: Marie Rose

107021.desc: Hehe… sometimes you can completely change the way people see you with just a simple change in attire. Don't you agree, Commander~? Don’t worry, I'm still your Lexington~
107021.name: The Beauty of Spring

301020.desc: Special Type I-class destroyer number two – Shirayuki.
301020.name: Shirayuki

101301.desc: Commander, g-good evening...? Right now, I'm bringing presents to Radford and the others...? Could you give me a hand? Th-thank you... Um, your present.. this apple, do you want it?
101301.name: Light of the Holiest Star

301110.desc: Type III Akatsuki-class destroyer number three - Ikazuchi.
301110.name: Ikazuchi

900301.desc: 请问，您就是“指挥官”吗？啊，太好了！初次见面，我是穗香！虽然不知道能帮忙到什么程度，不过我很擅长学习的~总之…请多指教！
900301.name: Honoka

405023.desc: They have a peculiar way of wishing a happy New Year in the Sakura Empire. In line with their traditions, I've put on this new outfit. I hope it doesn't... look strange on me. ...You like it? I see... That being the case, I'll keep wearing it for the time
405023.name: Seasonal Pine and the Frost Flower

301269.desc: Ariake-class destroyer, Yuugure, has completed retrofitting. Ehehe, from now on... Ariake and I will be in your care once more, Commander.
301269.name: Yuugure (Retrofit)

202030.desc: Leander-class light cruiser – Ajax, Hull Number 22!
202030.name: Ajax

101371.desc: Kalk, reporting in once again, now with a new outfit! Hehe... Commander, will you walk me to school?
101371.name: Snow Fairy Schoolgirl

301021.desc: Whoa now! There's enough food for everyone, so don't fight over it! ...Commander? Don't just stand there, give me a hand, please!
301021.name: Bunny Breeder

107051.desc: Hey, Commander, are you lost? How about a drink? ... Huh? Drunk? Me? Oh, Commander, you're such a card. This is just grape juice... isn't it?
107051.name: Evening I Can't Remember

405022.desc: I bet Bismarck must've been thinking about how to invite me to the party, but ended up asking you to do it, Commander. Hehe... Let's get going soon. It's best not to keep her waiting.
405022.name: Iron Blood Snowstorm

10100070.desc: I'm White Heart, the guardian CPU of Lowee. Pleased to meet you. I'm gonna give you a taste of a CPU's power!
10100070.name: White Heart

900317.desc: 新奥尔良级重巡洋舰——{namecode:195}，舷号CA-38
900317.name: San Francisco

10100030.desc: I'm Blanc. Nice to meet you. Maybe you could introduce some intriguing books from this world to me...
10100030.name: Blanc

10100051.desc: Oh, Commander? Won't you join me in a short conversation? I'll tell you things about Planeptune. Oh, and I'm eagerly awaiting the day you come to Planeptune for a visit.
10100051.name: Goddesses' Promise

301581.desc: It's my turn? Hold on... Umm, could you please not stare at me like that? It's... making me feel uncomfortable.
301581.name: Sports Festival Preparations

102093.desc: Good timing! I was just about to take my little buddy here out for a road trip! Commander, there's room for two if you want to come!
102093.name: Road Trip!

900304.desc: 你就是把海咲带来这个港口的人吧？是叫“指挥官”对么…哼，虽然不知道你是怎么把海咲骗来的，身为姐姐的我可没那么好对付。敢乱来的话，要你好看！…我的名字？…叫我凪咲就好了，你这“大笨狗”！
900304.name: Nagisa

304021.desc: Look how late it is... Commander, shall we embark on a dreamy voyage together?
304021.name: Moonlit Cruise

202031.desc: Ahaha, that slovenly expression on your face proves I made the right wardrobe choice♪ Now then, Commander, can I offer you some wine?
202031.name: Party Queen

10100071.desc: B-bastard! Where are you looking? I bet you're thinking I look like a kid! Eh....? They're just right? If Commander says something like that... I don't know how to react...
10100071.name: Goddesses' Humility

10100080.desc: I am the CPU of Leanbox, Green Heart. No matter who the enemy is, I will not hold back. Are you ready?
10100080.name: Green Heart

403038.desc: If fate brought us together, then it has my thanks… I look forward to our future together~
403038.name: Symphonic Fate

102163.desc: Oh, what a wonderful breeze. Maybe the windows ought always to be open during class... Commander? What are you standing around for? There's a vacant seat right here for you.
102163.name: A Breath of Fresh Air

204033.desc: Beauty is not always over the rainbow. Sometimes it is right in your backyard. Commander, how would you like to spend this quiet, lovely day right here with me?
204033.name: Dawnlight's Dame

306051.desc: Waaaah! My candy! Candy is spillin’ everywhere! ...Wh-why are y’all chasin’ me? Commander, help me catch the pumpkin!
306051.name: Patrolling Witch

101170.desc: Benson-class destroyer - Laffey, Hull Number DD-459!
101170.name: Laffey

303010.desc: First ship of the {namecode:53}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:53}.
303010.name: Furutaka

312014.desc: Hehehe, come on in, nya! Can I help you find something, nya? Your genial and knowledgeable staff, Akashi, will gladly provide her detailed recommendations, nya!
312014.name: Welcome to Sofmap!

403041.desc: For a servant, your eyes are good... *coughs*... I'm an Ironblood Princess, the Queen of Night, Deutschland! Servant? No. I am the first of my family. Come, kiss the ring of royalty!
403041.name: Dark Demon Princess

306050.desc: First ship of the {namecode:87}-class aircraft carriers, {namecode:87}.
306050.name: {namecode:87}

201039.desc: New outfit, new rigging, same ardent spirit! Ahaha, I'm serious~! Commander, thanks a lot~!
201039.name: Ardent (Retrofit)

10100081.desc: Commander, are you having a good time? Ehehe, I certainly am. It's not often that we get to relax like this. Why don't we head out and enjoy the breeze?
10100081.name: Goddesses' Moment

202032.desc: I have some special chocolate right here, just~ for~ you. Hehe, if you want it so badly... then come and get it~
202032.name: Valentine's Reward?

107050.desc: Yorktown-class aircraft carrier ー Yorktown, Hull Number CV-5!
107050.name: Yorktown

202280.desc: I am the light cruiser, Dido, currently taking part in idol activities as part of the experimental Muse System. I learned more or less what idols are supposed to do from the others, so p-please... keep a close eye on me!
202280.name: Dido µ

107061.desc: Merry Christmas, Commander! I shall be Santa Claus tonight, so make sure to hang up your stockings on the fireplace before going to sleep!
107061.name: Reindeer Master

900302.desc: 你就是这个港口的主人，也就是“指挥官”是吧？初次见面，我是霞。今后可能要在这里打扰一段时间，还请多多指教了——
900302.name: Kasumi

10500011.desc: Tada~! It's your favorite Shirakami Fubuki, Hololive Summer version! Commander, pleased to be your fox!
10500011.name: Beachside Fox

10500020.desc: Hey Commander, it's nice to meet you~! I'm Tokino Sora, a virtual idol affiliated with Hololive! I'll do my absolute best here like I always do! I'll be in your care, so cheer me on, Commander!
10500020.name: Tokino Sora

312012.desc: Heheh, this is what I've been saving up for, nya~♪ A special dress that combines Gothic fashion with Sakura charm! Commander, how about those gems, nya?
312012.name: The Black Cat Cometh!

301251.desc: Hope everyone enjoys the oodles of balloons I made for this party! Yeah, I'm sure the little girls will love 'em!
301251.name: Unending Friendship

705011.desc: You have my thanks for this exercise, comrade! I shall gladly carry out the important duty of judge, jury, and rehabilitator!
705011.name: Imposing Warden

301841.desc: Commander, over here! We're about to start without you! Ahaha, what would you like to do, Commander? Beach volleyball? Sandcastle building? We can also go relax in the water if you'd like!
301841.name: Suzutsuki, Beachside Attendant!

102094.desc: Happy New Year's, Commander! I heard everyone from the Sakura Empire was dressing like this, so... Hehehe, think this looks good on me? I thought I'd ask for your impression first, Commander.
102094.name: New Year's Challenge!

9707020.desc: Aircraft carrier Ark Royal, at your service. I hereby vow to lend you my strength for as long as you harbour honourable ambitions!
9707020.name: Ark Royal META

205048.desc: I never imagined that this dreamlike situation would come to pass... Commander, have you also been looking forward to sharing this moment with me? Hehe~

901021.desc: Commander, you're not going to get into the water? ...Ah, I'm fine right here. To tell you the truth, I once got washed away by the waves, and then got laughed at by Vauquelin... so I'm perfectly fine right here.

301611.desc: Learning is exciting. The joy of acquiring new knowledge, the sense of achievement from solving difficult problems... you'll understand once you try it. So, shall we study together, Commander?

206032.desc: This... present... is for you... I hope you like it... What? Me wearing this outfit is the best gift I can give you? Co... Commander!...

103069.desc: Nice to meet you, I'm Indianaportland! ... Hm? Who's Indy? She's my precious little sister, and my most beloved...
103069.name: Portland (Retrofit)

202020.desc: Leander-class light cruiser – Achilles, Hull Number 70!
202020.name: Achilles

10500041.desc: I'm the lovely high school girl, now in her extra-pure pajamas, Natsuiro Matsuri! Hey hey, Commander, what do you think? Surprised? Don't gawk at me too much~

301801.desc: All right, everything looks good! I'm super excited and my batteries are fully charged! I'm heading out~!

107049.desc: I didn't realize I could still become more powerful! I'll work harder from here on out to teach everyone how to fight!
107049.name: Ranger (Retrofit)

107035.desc: Merry Christmas! Here comes Christmas Sara, shining like a star in the silent night! Hehehe, how's that for a holiday greeting? So, have you decided where we're gonna spend our Christmas Eve yet?
107035.name: Silent Night Songstress

102273.desc: The annual moon gazing festival's upon us again~ Ah, so you know a thing or two about the Mid-Autumn Festival, Commander? Then I reckon you know what we're doing tonight, right~? ♡
102273.name: Moongazing on the 29½th

107229.desc: Light carrier Independence reporting. Retrofitting complete. I'm ready to take on harder, more vital missions. Leave anything like that to me.
107229.name: Independence (Retrofit)

101172.desc: Mmph... The waistline is too high... and a little too tight... The sleeves are too breezy cause they're so big... It's not like I wanted to change clothes, but... what do you think, Commander?
101172.name: Snow Rabbit and Candy Apple

206031.desc: Unicorn... is now a songstress... *giggles* Unicorn's song has reached Onii-chan's heart.
206031.name: Little Star Songstress

101400.desc: Farragut-class destroyer – Aylwin, Hull Number DD-355.
101400.name: Aylwin

207042.desc: Are you preparing to hold an event for the port? Hehe, sounds like you could use my help. Don't worry, with someone as beautiful as me around, anything you do will surely be blessed with success!
207042.name: Guidance of the Spring Goddess

102161.desc: Oh my, do I really look so unusual in this outfit? I want to be able to enjoy my day off as well, you know? Hehe, don't you think it feels nice to just sit back and take in the ocean breeze?

307049.desc: Retrofit complete! Aircraft Carrier Hiryuu, reporting for duty! Hahaha! I finally got the chance to use that line! I'll be counting on you once more!

206030.desc: Aircraft carrier – Unicorn, Hull Number I72!

201332.desc: "Let's go explore the ocean together! What special things will we be able to find today~?" Hehe, how's that, Commander?

101022.name: A Christmas Thank-You

301642.desc: Happy anniversary~ Today's a day to enjoy to yer heart's content, ya know? I'm just havin' fun in my own way, checkin' out cute girls from afar~ I appreciate yer concern though, Commander~

103132.desc: Oh crap! Move outta the way, Commander! Come on, man, look out next time! You'd have gotten hurt if I'd slammed into you!

205060.desc: King George V-class battleship – Prince of Wales, Hull Number 53!
